{"tid":646054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[創意台]找數; [時事台]五毛Me係鬼仔#99568底已起","createTime":"2018-04-28T17:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T10:12:38.000Z","uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"87334a5b1f9d6b5d65643736318de9c920f76da4","tid":646054,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"樓主已經退出左連登喇？<br />\n未裸跑喎<br />\n（1q題） 三頁內估中我永久退出連登同埋喺ifc裸跑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/645927/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/645927/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五毛Me係鬼仔#99568底已起<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/614130/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/614130/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[quote]事緣: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/590311/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/590311/page/1</a><br />\n會員on99屌喇星開post起鳩個小學雞底 由於睇唔過眼<br />\n亦見到佢自爆左youtube ac, 決定用少少時間試下起佢底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會員on99屌喇星 youtube ac: pc 9527<br />\n竟然連接左google+<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成功左第一步<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/103914_8254a4657f68510fb01fac469b5a9b42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F103914_8254a4657f68510fb01fac469b5a9b42.png&h=b2294ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但咁既資料太唔足夠 亦好容易起錯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再慢慢睇下youtube ac比到D咩我地 發現原來on99屌喇星upload過幾條片<br />\n其中一條<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104145_32d3ca5e23f4ccf1e4c8660c40e75f33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104145_32d3ca5e23f4ccf1e4c8660c40e75f33.png&h=2706f2b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104151_0a7b8575f81e6d28645879810e6f43a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104151_0a7b8575f81e6d28645879810e6f43a9.png&h=8b057f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信該留言者熟悉片主 亦都透露左pc 9527亦即係on99屌喇星叫Joe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我地就開始用google+比既資料去起底 <br />\n首先係Tam Hiu Sze小姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104408_bdd7c437366c101ea2b7ab2f606a469e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104408_bdd7c437366c101ea2b7ab2f606a469e.png&h=84ac15b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為左確保無搵錯人 我係Tam Hiu Sze小姐既friend list試下搵唔搵到common friend<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104435_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104435_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=b02aba47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果成功搵到Hoi Kit Leung<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104540_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104540_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=dc576784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再搵到Cody Lam<br />\n<br />\n已經代表無起錯 不過重點主角都係依位叫呀Joe既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104726_bbf4bbb47f12200df3f5be6765c24aad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104726_bbf4bbb47f12200df3f5be6765c24aad.png&h=bb2303cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104734_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104734_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=f2ead5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104740_e29efbe021d12549075b6b01f41993eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104740_e29efbe021d12549075b6b01f41993eb.jpg&h=0a176f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104747_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104747_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=0fc3268b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾位friend list都不約而同有依位Joe Lee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105148_a9fc6e56641b97a4f42197d18d69f16f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105148_a9fc6e56641b97a4f42197d18d69f16f.jpg&h=2fbbbffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而Joe Lee friend list亦都有Andy Lee <br />\n咁多資料加埋已經幾肯定會員on99屌喇星就係Joe Lee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再保守D 我地睇埋Joe Lee既Facebook<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105342_49829455611ff6eaed3d12c1c0468dd0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105342_49829455611ff6eaed3d12c1c0468dd0.png&h=d40766c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係倫敦讀緊書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105355_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105355_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=5724e527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105411_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105411_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=b7c5f033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦都同會員on99屌喇星一樣好關注時事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後就係會員on99屌喇星出場喇！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105515_20fd42213f37387d37674cc384319170.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105515_20fd42213f37387d37674cc384319170.png&h=cbc40d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105520_8cf4b6fc0feb75748a28801a6e7aa0d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105520_8cf4b6fc0feb75748a28801a6e7aa0d6.png&h=80ec764c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於無其他相 透過2張相既推測<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105551_c2e758ec1d4b65886c2e24eeddbe75c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105551_c2e758ec1d4b65886c2e24eeddbe75c2.jpg&h=4a54c7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會員on99屌喇星就係前排中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797562143da3e4dae062ee690c0477a416ae832c","tid":646054,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2934e731ade40ae94a3d97409d9cc3b08745e70b","tid":646054,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T19:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b0eaa334793a69cafc2665f0a676547a09acb2","tid":646054,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim